author: miketoole
title: Powerball $435 Million Winning Ticket Sold In Indiana; $1 Million Winner In Mass.
text:
BOSTON (CBS) – There was just one winning ticket sold in Wednesday night’s $435 million Powerball drawing and it was in Indiana.
The winning numbers were 10-13-28-52-61 with the Powerball 2.
Powerball drawing 2/22/17 (WBZ-TV graphic)
There was a $2 million Match 5 Power Play winner in New Jersey.
Four people won Match 5 $1 million prizes in Massachusetts, New York, Kansas and Texas.
There’s no word yet on where the Massachusetts ticket was sold.
The jackpot for the next drawing Saturday night now stands at $40 million.
